  "parent_id": null,
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Some local codes impose other restrictions and requirements and will in most cases take precedence over  other guidelines."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Avoid loops as explained in A.1 and shown in Figure A.4. Install instead as shown in Figure A.5."
    },
    {
      "type": "caption",
      "text": "Figure A.5  Earthing arrangement"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Arrange the high-voltage distribution bus bar system in such a way as to minimise the emission of magnetic  fields."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Avoid installing information technology equipment near to disturbing sources."
    }
